  "texts": [
    "This might reflect the students' need for specific coding knowledge and improvements to the AI-generated solutions.",
    "Additionally, prompts related to reviewing their own code, refining their own code, and debugging their own code (356 prompts in total; 14.91% of total prompts) demonstrate a lower reliance on ChatGPT, with students coding first and then utilizing AI for support.",
    "Based on the prompt labels described previously, five AI interaction profiles were identified across all sessions: AI-reliant code generator, AI-reliant code generator & refiner, AI-collaborative coder, AI-assisted code refiner, and AI-independent coder.",
    "The description of these profiles and their distributions across intervention sessions are given in Table 2.",
    "In the first session, majority of the students exhibited behaviors as AI-Reliant Code Generators (30.82%) and AI-Assisted Code Refiners (27.40%)."
